Description.Name: Part-y Time
Description.Details:
A few days later you arrive on the bridge to see Dr Murad working on the KF Console.  You walk over to Darius, "She still working on that Console?"

Darius nods, "They've been hard at work for the past few days installing the parts."

You look over at the astechs and Dr Murad busily connecting wires and components in the Console.  A few moments later, the last panel is bolted back in place and Dr Murad calls out to you, "Commander, the Console is fixed now.  Shall I activate it?"

Description.Name: Activate KF Console
Description.Details: Set Console to Active

Description.Name: Activate KF Console
Description.Details: "You ponder her query for a few minutes before responding, "Good work, Farah. Set the KF Console to ACTIVE and we will use a Pirate Point for our next jump." The KF Console is now online. STATUS: ACTIVE."
